        <p>Posts use Markdown with YAML frontmatter for metadata:</p>
        <pre><code>---
title: My Awesome Post
description: This is a great post
published: true
date: 2023-05-25
tags:
  - rails
  - ruby
---

# Post content starts here

Regular markdown content goes here...</code></pre>
      </div>
    </div>
